Kairana

Kairana is a city in Uttar Pradesh, in India.

GPS Coordinates of Kairana, Uttar Pradesh, India

Kairana is located on the latitude of 29.39541 and longitude of 77.2054 and has a geohash of ttnzhz728jwf.

Cities and Towns near Kairana

The nearest significant population center from Kairana is Samalkha in Haryana, India, located 25 kilometers or 16 miles ↙ SW of the city. Other locations in close proximity include Panipat (Haryana, India) located 27 km (17 mi) ↙ SW and Safidon (Haryana, India) located 51 km (32 mi) ← W of Kairana.
